1051
00:40:37,901 --> 00:40:40,612
[Laughs] Yeah, it's...
it's for your kids.

1052
00:40:40,654 --> 00:40:42,447
I just thought that
they might have fun with it.

1053
00:40:42,489 --> 00:40:43,448
"My kids."
Yeah.

1054
00:40:43,490 --> 00:40:44,949
Right, because before,

1055
00:40:44,991 --> 00:40:46,368
